com.hds.hcpaw.fss.api

Class AnywhereShareAPI

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hds.hcpaw.fss.api.AnywhereShareAPI

  • public class AnywhereShareAPI
extends java.lang.Object
    API for share activities such as create share, invite users, etc. These methods are implemented using the HCP Anywhere FSS API /fss/public/share URIs.

    See the method AnywhereAPI.getShareAPI() to obtain an instance of the AnywhereShareAPI.
